etomica.gaussianwork

Class MeterWorkABandReweighting

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.gaussianwork.MeterWorkABandReweighting
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataSource, IEtomicaDataSource

    public class MeterWorkABandReweighting
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEtomicaDataSource
    Meter used for multiharmonic overlap sampling in the A-sampled system. \ The meter measures the energy difference for the A and B potentials. the sampling of A gives us the information of a. < beta*U_AW >A : notation ---- [ betaUBAf_avg ] b. < beta*U_AW >W : notation ---- [ betaUBAr_avg ] ---------- U_AW = U_A - U_W output the probability distribution of the histogram for a. and b. Key: a. eA = e^(-beta*U_A) b. eB = e^(-beta*U_B) c. eW = e^(-beta*U_W)
